               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     Astronomical tables here entitled <title>Zīj-i Ūlūgh Bayg</title>, also known as <title>Zīj-i Sulṭānī-i Gūrkānī</title> records observations made at the
                     royal observatory in Samarqand in circa 1438, completed for the
                     Timurid-era Prince Ulugh Bayg (1394–1449). The work compiles observations made by Ūlūgh Bayg with the assistance of
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/73701246"
                        key="person_73701246" role="edt" change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup"
                        >Qāẓīzādah-’i Rūmī </persName>, subsequently edited by <persName
                        xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90047204"
                        key="person_90047204" role="edt" change="#role-assignment">Alī ibn
                           Muḥammad Qūshjī, (d. ca. 1475)</persName>. While unsigned and undated, this manuscript may be from the <placeName
                              cert="high" ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000208">Indian
                              subcontinent</placeName>, possibly completed during the <date cert="medium"
                                 calendar="#Gregorian" notBefore="1700" notAfter="1800">18th century CE</date>.</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_709-item1">
                     <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/66844656" key="person_66844656">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Ulugh Beg,
                           1394-1449</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Ūlūgh Bayg</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">اولوغ بیگ</persName>
                     </author>
                     <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/73701246" key="person_73701246"
                        role="edt ctb" change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Qāẓīzādah-’i Rūmī</persName>
                     </author>
                     <editor ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90047204" key="person_90047204"
                        role="edt ctb" change="#role-assignment">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Alī ibn Muḥammad Qūshjī, d. 1474 or 5
                        </persName>
                     </editor>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_1296" change="#ids-cleanup">Zīj-i
                        Ūlūgh Bayg</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_1296" change="#ids-cleanup">زيج اولوغ
                        بيگ</title>
                     <title type="alt" xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Zīj-i Sulṭānī-i Gūrkānī</title>
                     <title type="alt" xml:lang="fa">زیج سلطانی گورکانی</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa" type="basmala"><locus from="1b" to="1b"> برگ ۱پ (folio
                           1b):</locus> تبارك الذى جعل فى السماء بروجاً و جعل فيها سراجاً و قمراً و
                        منيراً مالك الملكى كه مصباح صباح و جعل الشمس سراجاً و هاجاً
                        افروخته...</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="233a" to="233a"> برگ ۲۳۳ر (folio 233a):</locus> و درمبداء اين
                        از تاريخ ملكي بالصد و هشتاد سال از يالهاي افتاب گذاشته بوده است و الله اعلم
                        بالصواب. </explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa">‌No colophon. </colophon>

                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>See <persName role="trl" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/49603196"
                           key="person_49603196">E. B. Knobel</persName>'s translation for an
                        analysis of this manuscript in comparison to other surviving copies held in
                        Britain.</note>
                  </msItem>
